  m_text: 'To win the game, destroy All the bricks by throwing orbs at them. Collect
    fragments of shattered bricks with your body to earn points. If you run out of
    orbs, or fail to break all the bricks before the time runs out, you lose the
    game. Use your hands to throw and catch orbs, or pick up the racket and use that
    to hit the orbs instead! New orbs to throw and your racket appear on your sides.

